@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Settings";
}
<div class="main-content">
    <div class="wrap-content container " id="container">
        <h1>Index</h1>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>Website Structure:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>URL structure: Ensure clear and descriptive URLs.</li>
                    <li>Navigation: Check for user-friendly navigation and logical site structure.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>Keyword Analysis:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Target keywords: Identify the primary and secondary keywords relevant to your content.</li>
                    <li>Keyword density: Evaluate the frequency of target keywords in content.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>Content Quality:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Unique and relevant content: Ensure that your content is valuable, unique, and relevant to your target audience.</li>
                    <li>Meta tags: Optimize title tags and meta descriptions for each page.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>On-Page SEO:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Header tags: Proper use of H1, H2, and H3 tags.</li>
                    <li>Image optimization: Optimize image alt text and file names.</li>
                    <li>Internal linking: Ensure proper linking within your site.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>Technical SEO:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Page load speed: Check and optimize for fast page loading.</li>
                    <li>Mobile responsiveness: Ensure your site is mobile-friendly.</li>
                    <li>XML sitemap: Have an updated XML sitemap to help search engines understand your site structure.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>Backlink Profile:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Backlinks: Analyze the quality and quantity of backlinks to your site.</li>
                    <li>Link building: Implement a strategy for acquiring high-quality backlinks.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>User Experience:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>User engagement metrics: Monitor bounce rate, time on site, and other user behavior metrics.</li>
                    <li>Mobile usability: Check for a positive mobile user experience.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>Analytics and Tracking:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Install Google Analytics: Set up Google Analytics to track website performance.</li>
                    <li>Google Search Console: Verify your site with Google Search Console to access additional insights.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>Social Media Integration:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul><li>Social signals: Integrate social media platforms and encourage social sharing.</li></ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <strong>Local SEO (if applicable):</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Local business information: Ensure accurate and consistent NAP (Name, Address, Phone) data.</li>
                    <li>Google My Business: Optimize your Google My Business listing.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>